{"tid":251172,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"全盛時期嘅PA WORKS真係好高質","createTime":"2017-05-20T16:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T11:15:38.000Z","uid":4493,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0df239772290425f6d3f9b2a9a8e43185c3c3612","tid":251172,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6MffR9xOLIM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6MffR9xOLIM&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=333cbce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6MffR9xOLIM</a><br />\n<br />\n每次睇返花開個Op2都搵到新嘅細節<br />\n一開始月台上面隻蝴蝶 追緒花隻雀 都係睇咗好多次之後先發覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係靚過好多劇場版同埋OVA 同埋有一個真真正正嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  後來劇場版都唔會接落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解後來嘅作品做唔到咁？真係好鍾意花開個風格 冇白箱咁寫實 又冇風平浪靜咁虛幻 真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a16cb3c8cdb343b43e60bc00d8bec7b839a35f5","tid":251172,"uid":53654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"花開話晒都係PA既周年紀念作<br />\n單講畫絕對係PA既最高規格"},{"pid":"9bfd365d037be1ecda5cc8466e711da8e15f78b8","tid":251172,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0975aa866c77e18f11587f5dc6c0216b552c0ba7","tid":251172,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>花開話晒都係PA既周年紀念作<br />\n單講畫絕對係PA既最高規格</blockquote><br />\n唔知2021年嗰套會有幾正呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d423ce0e3bf93883fe95371cf8ec00038fef359f","tid":251172,"uid":22018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"2482c9719d16d4da0277c3b19e0fead574f